items.title: IndusInd Bank Q1 Preview: Profit seen falling up to 91% YoY amid derivative loss overhang; 7 things to watch out for
items.description: IndusInd Bank will announce its Q1 earnings on Monday, July 28, where the private lender is expected to report a sharp decline in its year-on-year net profit driven by elevated provisioning, MFI stress, and weak loan/deposit growth.
